# ğŸ§© ConfigMaps aur Secrets

---

## ğŸ“˜ Conceptual Explanation

**ConfigMap**: Kubernetes ka ek object hai jo application ke liye **configuration data** store karta hai jaise environment variables.
**Secret**: Secure tarike se **sensitive information** (jaise passwords, API keys) store karne ke liye use hota hai.

---

## ğŸ§  Roman Urdu Explanation

ConfigMap mein hum non-sensitive data store karte hain (jaise `APP_MODE`), jabke Secret mein sensitive info (jaise `passwords`, `API keys`) securely rakhi jati hai.

